node.text:
So you've probably heard that Cyberpunk 2077 dropped last night but did you know you could win the real life car from the game?? Thanks to my friends at @rockstarenergy this epic build dubbed the Quadra could be yours. All you have to do is purchase one of the special Cyberpunk x Rockstar edition cans, crack the tab and enter the code at www.2077.rockstarenergy.com. 

Don't miss your shot at this build by the rad dudes at the @therockstargarage here in Southern California. 

@mrnicashby @therockstargarage @rockstarenergy 

#rockstarenergy #cyberpunk2077#Quadra#rockstargarage#giveaway

node.text: Huge thanks to @ToyotaUSA for dropping off the brand new #Corolla Apex! I had the pleasure of being one of the first to test drive this beauty on the streets of LA. Lots of awesome features like the Black and Bronze body kit, 18" flow formed wheels, lowered track tuned suspension, a fresh bronze stitched interior and more 💪🏼. Check it out. #ad  #LetsGoPlaces

node.text: #PickeringPaving adding 8K sqft to the #NHdrifthouse driveway💪🏼 prep today and asphalt tomorrow 🤘🏼🏎💨 #RT411

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Ryan Tuerck in New Hampshire with @zach.jopson. May be an image of grass.

node.text: I’ve been waiting to get this done all summer. 8K sqft pad going down with #PickeringPaving. Stoked boys!💪🏼 #NHdrifthouse getting it’s first major fun mod 🤘🏼🏎💨 #RT411 #somuchroomforactivities Massive thanks to @zach.jopson for coming out to shoot. Asphalt Vlog coming soon.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Ryan Tuerck on August 02, 2021 tagging @formulad, @dominant_engineering, @hartsock_motorsports, @johnreedracing, and @blackflagracingco. May be an image of 4 people and people standing.

node.text: Massive thanks to this team. Non-stop pushing all weekend to make our car the best it could be. One of the best weekends I’ve had working together on car setup. We never settled for “good”. These dudes made the car unbelievable to drive. Two team members not pictured, @johnreedracing and my wonderful wife #ShannyPants. #FDSEA @blackflagracingco @hartsock_motorsports @dominant_engineering 💪🏼 🙏🏻
